---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Strategic Reset Intensive — Structural Burnout, AI Strain, and Leadership Recalibration"
  description="A Strategic Transformations intensive for women navigating over-responsibility, under-support, and structural strain in the AI era."
  section="st"
  accentColor="teal"
>
  <section class="relative min-h-[78vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-st-gradient"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 82% 32%, rgba(13,148,136,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.08]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, rgba(255,255,255,0.6) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"></div>
    <div class="absolute right-[-6rem] top-20 h-64 w-64 rotate-12 border border-teal-DEFAULT/20" style="clip-path: polygon(25% 6.7%, 75% 6.7%, 100% 50%, 75% 93.3%, 25% 93.3%, 0% 50%);"></div>
    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-teal-DEFAULT"></div>

    <div class="container-wide relative z-10 py-24">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="st-tag inline-flex">Strategic Transformations</span>
          <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-muted border border-border rounded-full px-3 py-1">URI-rooted leadership architecture</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl text-light font-bold leading-tight mb-6 animate-on-scroll">
          A Strategic Reset Intensive for women who refuse to be the
          <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT italic">load-bearing wall</span>
          of the AI era.
        </h1>

        <p class="text-light text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mb-4 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.08s">
          For women navigating over-responsibility, under-support, and the pressure to keep performing in systems that were never designed for their sustainability.
        </p>

        <p class="text-muted text-base leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mb-8 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.12s">
          You will leave with a personal AI governance boundary, a practical AI operating system, and an execution plan that turns uncertainty into movement without sacrificing your nervous system, your integrity, or your voice.
        </p>

        <div class="mb-8 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.16s">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-muted mb-2">A Strategic Transformations diagnostic experience</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-light">Rooted in the liberation-centered leadership architecture of URI</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
          <a href="mailto:hello@nikkicates.com?subject=Strategic%20Reset%20Intensive%20Inquiry" class="btn-teal">Request the Intensive</a>
          <a href="#diagnostic" class="btn-outline-teal">See if this is for you</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="diagnostic" class="section-pad bg-[#0c1525]">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">What this names</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light">This is not generic burnout support.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        {[
          'You are being held responsible for more outcomes than you have the authority, support, or decision rights to carry.',
          'You are absorbing hidden labor, cleanup work, and emotional strain that rarely gets named and almost never gets resourced.',
          'You may be performing competence inside systems that depend on your overfunctioning.',
          'AI may be increasing the speed, noise, and oversight demands without reducing the burden on your body, judgment, or capacity.',
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="mb-4 h-10 w-10 border border-teal-DEFAULT/40 bg-teal-DEFAULT/5" style="clip-path: polygon(25% 6.7%, 75% 6.7%, 100% 50%, 75% 93.3%, 25% 93.3%, 0% 50%);"></div>
            <p class="text-light leading-relaxed">{item}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 70% at 50% 50%, rgba(13,148,136,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
    <div class="container-wide relative z-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <span class="st-tag mb-5 inline-flex">What you walk away with</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light mb-6">Clarity, boundaries, and a way forward.</h2>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The Strategic Reset Intensive is designed to help you distinguish what is personal, what is structural, what is recoverable, and what must be renegotiated.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
            This is a focused reset for women navigating burnout, reinvention, leadership strain, or career transition in the AI era. It combines diagnostic clarity, justice-centered language, and practical strategy so you can move forward without disappearing inside the system.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.12s">
          {[
            {
              title: 'Personal AI Governance Boundary',
              desc: 'A clear boundary for how you will and will not engage AI, speed, availability, and digital overreach in this season.'
            },
            {
              title: 'Practical AI Operating System',
              desc: 'A grounded approach to using AI as support rather than extraction, including where it helps, where it harms, and what needs guardrails.'
            },
            {
              title: 'Execution Plan',
              desc: 'A concrete next-step plan that identifies what to stop carrying, what to restructure, and what to move on immediately.'
            },
            {
              title: 'Included Resource',
              desc: 'The UNMASK Blueprint Vol. 1: Deconstruction of the Grind, including the accompanying interactive web experience.'
            },
          ].map((item) => (
            <div class="p-5 rounded-md border border-border hover:border-teal-DEFAULT/40 transition-colors bg-surface/50">
              <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold text-lg mb-2">{item.title}</p>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad bg-[#0c1525]">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">What’s included</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light">A focused, high-clarity engagement.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll">
          <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-3">Phase 1</p>
          <p class="font-heading text-light text-xl mb-3">Pre-work + Intake</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">A short diagnostic and intake reflection to surface where burnout, masking, authority mismatch, hidden labor, and AI strain are most active.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll">
          <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-3">Phase 2</p>
          <p class="font-heading text-light text-xl mb-3">Reset Session</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">A strategic deep-dive session focused on naming structural strain, clarifying your current reality, and identifying the highest-leverage moves forward.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll">
          <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-3">Phase 3</p>
          <p class="font-heading text-light text-xl mb-3">Reset Deliverables</p>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">A written reset summary with your AI governance boundary, practical operating system, execution priorities, and next-step recommendations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <span class="st-tag mb-5 inline-flex">Best fit</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light mb-6">This intensive is for you if…</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-muted">
            <p>• You are navigating burnout, transition, or reinvention and need more than encouragement.</p>
            <p>• You have been carrying too much without enough authority, support, or relief.</p>
            <p>• You suspect the issue is structural, but need language, boundaries, and a plan.</p>
            <p>• You want to engage AI without letting it erase your judgment, humanity, or voice.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
          <span class="st-tag mb-5 inline-flex">Investment</span>
          <div class="card border-teal-DEFAULT/30 bg-teal-DEFAULT/5">
            <p class="text-muted text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-3">Starting at</p>
            <p class="font-heading text-light text-5xl mb-4">$750</p>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Includes the diagnostic process, live reset session, written reset deliverable, and UNMASK Blueprint Vol. 1 with its companion experience.
            </p>
            <a href="mailto:hello@nikkicates.com?subject=Strategic%20Reset%20Intensive%20Inquiry" class="btn-teal w-full text-center">Inquire About the Intensive</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 relative overflow-hidden bg-[#0c1525]">
    <div class="container-mid relative z-10 text-center animate-on-scroll">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light mb-4">The next step is not more self-blame.</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        It is a Strategic Reset that helps you identify what is structural, what is recoverable, and what must change so your next season is built with more truth, more clarity, and more sovereignty.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="mailto:hello@nikkicates.com?subject=Strategic%20Reset%20Intensive%20Inquiry" class="btn-teal">Request the Intensive</a>
        <a href="/books/" class="btn-outline-teal">Explore the UNMASK Blueprint</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
